---
title: Toasted Sesame-Gochujang Bowls with Farro and Plant-Based Protein
description: No meat, no problem! Tonight's veggie dish is inspired by the Korean classic, bibimbap. This version uses farro instead of rice and subs in a savoury plant-based protein crumble that is pan-fried with aromatic sesame oil and gochujang. We know you'll be adding this to your Meatless Monday lineup!
